        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PHILOSOPHY -->
    <section class="philosophy" id="philosophy">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="philosophy-grid">
                <div class="philosophy-text">
                    <p class="section-label reveal">Our Philosophy</p>
                    <h2 class="section-title reveal">Welcome to <span class="gold-shimmer">Asian Man Tantric</span></h2>
                    <div class="gold-divider reveal"></div>
                    <p class="reveal">Asian Man Tantric is a renowned tantric massage service in London, dedicated to providing the finest holistic experience for men. We believe that true relaxation transcends the physical &mdash; it is a journey that harmonises body, mind and spirit.</p>
                    <p class="reveal">Our skilled masseurs are professionally trained in the ancient arts of tantric bodywork, combining Eastern wisdom with modern therapeutic techniques. Every session is conducted with the utmost discretion, respect, and attention to your individual needs.</p>
                    <p class="reveal">Whether you seek relief from the pressures of modern life, a deeper connection with your own body, or a transformative sensual experience, our sanctuary in the heart of London awaits you.</p>
                    <div class="philosophy-stats reveal">
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <h3>5+</h3>
                            <p>Years Experience</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
                            <h3>2000+</h3>
                            <p>Happy Clients</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-item">
