                        <p>An intimate, deeply connecting experience where skilled touch and body-to-body contact awaken your senses and guide you into a profound state of relaxation and bliss.</p>
                        <span class="service-price">From &pound;200 <span>/ session</span></span>
                        <a href="#booking" class="service-btn">Book Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <!-- Service 3 -->
