                    <!-- Slide 5 -->
                    <div class="testimonial-slide">
                        <div class="testimonial-card">
                            <div class="testimonial-stars">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="testimonial-quote">Best massage experience I have ever had in London. The body-to-body technique was performed with incredible professionalism. You can tell the masseur has years of dedicated training. Will definitely return.</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Martin J" class="testimonial-avatar">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="testimonial-name">Martin J.</p>
                                    <p class="testimonial-location">Verified Client</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Slide 6 -->
                    <div class="testimonial-slide">
                        <div class="testimonial-card">
                            <div class="testimonial-stars">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="testimonial-quote">I was nervous at first, but the warm welcome and professional approach immediately put me at ease. The experience was deeply healing and I felt completely safe throughout. Absolutely wonderful.</p>
                            <div class="testimonial-author">
                                <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Sebastine" class="testimonial-avatar">
                                <div>
                                    <p class="testimonial-name">Sebastine</p>
                                    <p class="testimonial-location">Verified Client</p>
                                </div>
