                        <div class="testimonial-card">
                            <div class="testimonial-stars">
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
                            </div>
                            <p class="testimonial-quote">Exceptional from start to finish. The environment was spotlessly clean, the oils were premium quality, and the massage itself was a genuine work of art. This is luxury at its finest.</p>
