            <div style="text-align:center;padding:12px 0;margin-top:16px;border-top:1px solid rgba(201,169,110,0.08)">
                <a href="https://www.heyboss.com.tw/" target="_blank" style="color:rgba(201,169,110,0.5);font-size:12px;text-decoration:none;letter-spacing:1px;font-family:Inter,sans-serif">Built with AI by <span style="color:rgba(201,169,110,0.8);font-weight:600">HEY!BOSS</span> 銀月數位顧問</a>
            </div>
